<div class="header">
	<h3>Welcome to Numerology App</h3>
	<hr />
</div>

<div class="jumbotron">
	This Numerology App is based on the birth path number! The birth path number is determined by doing a little bit of math magic with your date of birth. Your birthdate is reduced down to a single digit, 1-9. That number corresponds to a specific message about your path in life and place in the world. 
